column5: just wondering if anyone has been out on the ice between Georgina and Thorah.Is it safe at this point?
I wasn 't out there myself, but I saw a lot of huts and machines out there yesterday from where I was. The ice has smoothed down a bit, but some places are REALLY rough going.  Ice was about 8"  s.
thanks for the report ,looking to head up there Feb 5
